1
00:00:00,940 --> 00:00:03,530
Selamat datang ke pembentangan 
tentang "Pendaraban"

2
00:00:03,530 --> 00:00:05,270
dan "Pembahagian Nombor Negatif".

3
00:00:05,270 --> 00:00:06,750
Mari kita mulakan.

4
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:08,920
Anda akan dapati bahawa Pendaraban

5
00:00:08,920 --> 00:00:10,730
dan Pembahagian nombor negatif

6
00:00:10,760 --> 00:00:13,870
lebih senang dari yang anda sangka.

7
00:00:13,867 --> 00:00:16,167
Anda cuma perlu ingat beberapa peraturan saja.

8
00:00:20,994 --> 00:00:25,224
Apabila 2 nombor negatif didarabkan,

9
00:00:25,220 --> 00:00:31,790
contohnya (-2) x (-2);

10
00:00:31,790 --> 00:00:33,970
Mula-mula anggapkan tiada 
tanda negatif (-)

11
00:00:33,970 --> 00:00:35,240
pada nombor-nombor itu.

12
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:40,150
Jadi 2 x 2 = 4.

13
00:00:40,150 --> 00:00:42,670
Bila nombor negatif didarabkan bersama,

14
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:45,180
jawapannya ialah positif (+).

15
00:00:45,175 --> 00:00:47,715
Jadi tuliskan peraturan pertama ini.

16
00:00:47,710 --> 00:00:54,290
(-) x (-) = (+).

17
00:00:56,854 --> 00:01:01,894
Bagaimana pula dengan (-2) x 2 = ?

18
00:01:01,892 --> 00:01:04,772
Mula-mula, anggapkan tiada tanda negatif (-)

19
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:06,060
pada nombor-nombor itu.

20
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:10,170
2 x 2 = 4.

21
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:13,740
Kita ada (-2) x (+2);

22
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:15,910
bila nombor (-) didarabkan dengan nombor (+),

23
00:01:15,910 --> 00:01:18,920
jawapannya ialah (-).

24
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:20,260
Ini ialah peraturan kedua.

25
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:29,010
(-) x (+) = (-)

26
00:01:29,009 --> 00:01:34,789
Bagaimana pula jika 2 x (-2) ?

27
00:01:34,786 --> 00:01:37,136
Saya rasa anda boleh teka jawapannya

28
00:01:37,140 --> 00:01:41,170
sebab hampir sama dengan contoh tadi.

29
00:01:41,170 --> 00:01:44,800
Ini dipanggil "Penukaran Tertib" atau

30
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:45,860
"Commutative Property" dalam Bahasa Inggeris.

31
00:01:47,700 --> 00:01:51,780
2 x (-2) = (-4)

32
00:01:51,780 --> 00:01:57,640
Maka peraturan yang terakhir ialah

33
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,980
(+) x (-) = (-)

34
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:01,490
2 peraturan terakhir ini

35
00:02:03,985 --> 00:02:04,995
sebenarnya sama saja.

36
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:07,570
(-) x (+) = (-), 
atau

37
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:09,140
(+) x (-) = (-)

38
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:13,730
Juga boleh dinyatakan,
jika nombor berbeza 'tanda' didarabkan,

39
00:02:13,730 --> 00:02:16,400
jawapannya ialah negatif (-).

40
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,890
Dan semestinya anda tahu apa jawapannya

41
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:21,550
jika nombor positif didarabkan bersama;

42
00:02:21,550 --> 00:02:22,840
anda akan dapat nombor positif (+).

43
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,900
Jom kita imbas kembali.

44
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:27,970
(-) x (-) = (+)

45
00:02:27,970 --> 00:02:30,390
(-) x (+) = (-)

46
00:02:30,390 --> 00:02:32,730
(+) x (-) = (-)

47
00:02:32,730 --> 00:02:36,290
Dan (+) x (+) = (+)

48
00:02:36,290 --> 00:02:39,980
Mungkin anda sedikit keliru,

49
00:02:39,980 --> 00:02:42,270
jadi saya permudahkan untuk anda.

50
00:02:42,270 --> 00:02:46,350
Bila anda mendarab nombor-nombor

51
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:55,180
yang sama 'tanda'; anda dapat jawapan positif (+).

52
00:02:55,175 --> 00:02:57,845
yang berlainan 'tanda'; anda dapat jawapan negatif (-).

53
00:03:11,010 --> 00:03:17,780
Contohnya, 
1 x 1 = 1,

54
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:22,120
ataupun
(-1) x (-1) = 1

55
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:29,150
Ini pula,
1 x (-1) = (-1)

56
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:32,600
ataupun
(-1) x 1 = (-1).

57
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:36,130
Perhatikan, ada 2 'tanda' pada latihan di bawah;

58
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:38,590
(+) 1 dan 
(-1).

59
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:41,120
Dan pada latihan di atas
di sebelah sini,

60
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,680
kedua-dua nombor 1 bertanda (+).

61
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:45,970
Di sebelah sini pula bertanda (-).

62
00:03:45,970 --> 00:03:49,110
Sekarang mari kita buat sedikit latihan

63
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:51,510
supaya anda boleh cuba contoh-contoh ini,

64
00:03:51,510 --> 00:03:56,200
dan 'tips' serta peraturan yang membantu anda.

65
00:04:02,855 --> 00:04:06,755
Contoh;
(-4) x 3,

66
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:11,820
4 x 3 = 12,
di sini ada tanda (-) dan (+).

67
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:15,670
Tanda berlainan;
jawapannya (-).

68
00:04:15,670 --> 00:04:19,060
Maka (-4) x 3 = (-12).

69
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:21,310
Ini logik sebab asasnya,

70
00:04:21,310 --> 00:04:25,070
(-4) x 3 sama dengan,

71
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,800
(-4) + (-4) + (-4) = (-12)!

72
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:31,120
Anda boleh rujuk dalam video

73
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:34,200
"Penambahan &amp; Penolakan Nombor Negatif".

74
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,210
Jom selesaikan 1 latihan lagi.

75
00:04:35,210 --> 00:04:40,430
(-2) x (-7) = ?

76
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:42,470
Anda boleh hentikan video ini seketika

77
00:04:42,470 --> 00:04:44,030
untuk cuba selesaikan sendiri

78
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,420
dan semak jawapannya kemudian.

79
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:51,190
2 x 7 = 14,
dan semua nombor sama tanda,

80
00:04:51,190 --> 00:04:53,530
jadi jawapannya (+14). 
Biasanya tanda (+) tidak ditulis,

81
00:04:53,530 --> 00:04:56,930
ini cuma untuk pemahaman anda.

82
00:04:56,930 --> 00:05:05,880
Bagaimana pula dengan
9 x (-5) = ?

83
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:08,800
9 x 5 = 45,

84
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:13,660
Perhatikan,tandanya berlainan.

85
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:18,010
Jadi 9 x (-5) = (-45)

86
00:05:18,010 --> 00:05:24,540
Seterusnya,
(-6) x (-11) = ?

87
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:29,730
6 x 11 = 66,
ada tanda (-)

88
00:05:29,730 --> 00:05:31,720
dan (-) juga,
jadi jawapannya (+).

89
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,910
Sekarang,saya nak berikan anda ujian.

90
00:05:32,910 --> 00:05:39,100
Berapakah jawapan
0 x (-12) = ?

91
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:42,740
Anda boleh rujuk pada tanda berlainan di sini,

92
00:05:42,740 --> 00:05:46,460
tapi sebenarnya,
0 bukan nombor (+) atau (-).

93
00:05:46,460 --> 00:05:48,320
Apa saja nombor yang didarabkan dengan 0,
jawapannya ialah 0.

94
00:05:48,315 --> 00:05:52,085
Samada nombor itu (-) atau (+).

95
00:05:53,650 --> 00:05:57,630
bila darab 0 jawapannya ialah 0.

96
00:05:57,630 --> 00:06:00,020
Sekarang, mari kita tengok samada

97
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:03,080
peraturan yang sama boleh diguna untuk "Pembahagian".

98
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:09,030
Contoh:
9 ÷ (-3) = ?

99
00:06:09,030 --> 00:06:11,820
9 ÷ 3 = 3,

100
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:13,640
Nombor-nombor ini berlainan tanda,

101
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:17,920
iaitu 9 dan (-3).

102
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:22,190
Tanda berlainan jawapannya (-).

103
00:06:22,190 --> 00:06:27,520
Jadi
9 ÷ (-3) = (-3).

104
00:06:27,520 --> 00:06:33,830
Bagaimana pula
(-16) ÷ 8 = ?

105
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:37,790
Anda tahu 
16 ÷ 8 = 2,

106
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:39,370
tetapi lihat tandanya berlainan.

107
00:06:39,370 --> 00:06:44,830
Maka,
(-16) ÷ 8 = (-2).

108
00:06:44,830 --> 00:06:49,140
Ingat ya, 
tanda berlainan jawapannya (-).

109
00:06:49,140 --> 00:07:00,500
Apakah jawapan
(-54) ÷ (-6) = ?

110
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:04,320
54 ÷ 6 = 9,

111
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:09,050
Kedua-dua "Pembahagi" dan 'yang dibahagi'

112
00:07:11,470 --> 00:07:13,890
bertanda (-);
(-54) dan (-6),

113
00:07:13,930 --> 00:07:18,190
maka jawapannya ialah (+).

114
00:07:18,193 --> 00:07:18,983
Tanda sama jawapannya (+).

115
00:07:24,730 --> 00:07:30,500
0 ÷ (-1) = 0

116
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:31,510
Mudah saja,

117
00:07:31,510 --> 00:07:33,200
sebab 0 bahagi apa saja nombor
jawapannya 0.

118
00:07:36,210 --> 00:07:38,420
Mari cuba 1 lagi latihan.

119
00:07:41,890 --> 00:07:44,930
4 ÷ (-1) = ?

120
00:07:44,930 --> 00:07:50,610
4 ÷ 1 = 4,
tetapi lihat tandanya berlainan.

121
00:07:50,610 --> 00:07:53,130
Jadi 
4 ÷ (-1) = (-4).

122
00:07:53,130 --> 00:07:54,410
Saya harap latihan tadi

123
00:07:54,410 --> 00:07:56,870
dapat membantu anda.

124
00:07:56,865 --> 00:08:01,385
Lakukan sebanyak mungkin latihan 
"Pendaraban &amp; Pembahagian Nombor Negatif".

125
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:03,010
Klik pada tanda "Hints"

126
00:08:03,010 --> 00:08:04,260
dan anda boleh rujuk peraturan untuk digunakan.

127
00:08:04,260 --> 00:08:09,450
Anda mungkin terfikir 
bagaimana peraturan tadi terjadi,

128
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:11,460
dan apa sebenarnya maksud pendaraban

129
00:08:11,459 --> 00:08:15,319
nombor (-) dengan nombor (+).

130
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,980
Dan pendaraban nombor (-)

131
00:08:16,982 --> 00:08:20,232
dengan nombor (-) juga.

132
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:29,020
Selamat maju jaya!

